name: The Chicken Destiny
description: I cried because I'm happy. It's my destiny as a chicken who created by God as food for humans consumption. I was created to make people full of protein, nutrition & happy. Not only me but all of God's creation in this world. Everything for humans life to be very happy. But please, it's a message for all humans in this world. Don't hurt and exploit us also this nature. Stop exploiting natural resources too much. Take good care and wisdom to the nature for better future.
